这是关于本人的一次推荐系统的尝试

该推荐系统使用java和Android分别模拟了移动端和客户端，注意是模拟因此外观简陋，只提供了数据收集和展示的功能，当然还写死了几个用户账户

该推荐系统使用的XGB+FFM模型

该推荐系统使用python构建核心的数据处理和模型训练文件

该系统使用MYSQL和BMOB作为web端和移动端的数据库

最后关于交互方面，与web端的交互使用了命令行函数，Android端的交互通过java作为中转

This is an attempt on my recommendation system.

The recommendation system uses Java and Android to simulate the mobile and client sides respectively. 
Note that the simulation is so crude that it only provides the functions of data collection and display. Of course, it also writes several user accounts dead.

XGB + FFM model used in this recommendation system

The recommendation system uses pythons to construct core data processing and model training files.

The system uses MYSQL and BMOB as the database of web and mobile end.

Finally, in terms of interaction, the command line functions are used for interaction with the web side, 
and the java used for Android interaction is used as a transit.
